{
  "texts": [
    "We observe that vocabulary adaptation leads to performance improvement in terms of Rouge-L for Llama-2 and Llama-3.1 in seven out of eight settings (except for Llama-2 on EBM dataset).",
    "In terms of Concept-Score which is a proxy measure for faithfulness (Zhang et al., 2023), Figure 2 shows that at least one vocabulary adaptation performs the best in five out of six settings, except for Llama-3.1 on PubMedQA dataset.",
    "We focus on the fine-grained analysis of LLMs in high OOV and high novelty data points.",
    "The Rouge-LCS values observed for each such category are reported in Table 6.",
    "In total, we benchmark an LLM on 48 settings: 32 OOV-related settings and 16 novelty-related settings."
  ]
}